r=Zhang Yi|date=2017-05-22|access-date=2018-01-06|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170529031151/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1048021.shtml|archive-date=2017-05-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hongkongfp.com/2017/05/20/curious-rise-white-left-chinese-internet-insult/|script-title=en:The curious rise of the ‘white left’ as a Chinese internet insult|date=2017-05-20|work=Hong Kong Free Press HKFP|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212193107/https://www.hongkongfp.com/2017/05/20/curious-rise-white-left-chinese-internet-insult/|archivedate=2017-12-12|df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://eastwest.eu/it/opinioni/sogno-cinese/cina-tra-alt-right-e-populismi-la-gente-contro-i-radical-chic|title=Cina tra Alt-right e populismi: la gente contro i radical chic|last=Pieranni|first=Simone|access-date=2017-12-11|language=it|date=2017-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703224614/http://eastwest.eu/it/opinioni/sogno-cinese/cina-tra-alt-right-e-populismi-la-gente-contro-i-radical-chic|archivedate=2017-07-03}}</ref>。

